title: Mug Cakes, Cupcakes and More! ~ Cath Kidston [Shades]epub
description:
Mug Cakes, Cupcakes and More! by Cath Kidston, Anna Burges-Lumsden 

Publisher: Quadrille Publishing Ltd (June 15, 2017)
ISBN-10: 1787130169
ISBN-13: 978-1787130166


Mug cakes are the hot baking trend for everyone who wants to whip up quick, delicious treats with minimum fuss. Simple and fast, all you need is a (Cath Kidston) mug and a microwave! For those who prefer to spend a bit more time in the kitchen, there are also recipes for easy cupcakes, delicious brownies, and one or two larger cakes
